{
  "page": "Runciter",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Grand Maester</span><br />Runciter</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">The Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_112_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">112&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Runciter</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> during the late reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> and the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Runciter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Runciter was appointed in <a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101&#160;AC</a> after the death of Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Allar\" title=\"Allar\">Allar</a>. He had only been in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> a short time before Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a> fell ill, complaining of severe pain in his stomach. Runciter treated Baelon and was able to bring his fever down and eased his pain with <a href=\"/index.php/Milk_of_the_poppy\" title=\"Milk of the poppy\">milk of the poppy</a>, but the prince's condition continued to worsen until he died on the fifth day of his <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>. Runciter opened the corpse and attributed the prince's death to a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Appendicitis\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Appendicitis\">burst belly</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Runciter later served King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a> after Jaehaerys passed away in <a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> In his records, he only cites a quarrel with King Viserys as the reason for Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>'s second exile.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He died in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_112_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">112&#160;AC</a> and was replaced by Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Mellos\" title=\"Mellos\">Mellos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Runciter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Heirs of the Dragon - A Question of Succession.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Penguin Random House: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/EXZE_KQnat4\">A Conversation with George R R Martin</a> (at 17min56s)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Allar\" title=\"Allar\">Allar</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>9th <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_112_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">112&#160;AC</a>        <br /><small>Served under: <b><a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a></b></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Mellos\" title=\"Mellos\">Mellos</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Grand_Maester\" title=\"Template:Grand Maester\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Grand_Maester&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Grand Maester (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Grand_Maester&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maesters</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Grand Maesters<br />to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ollidar\" title=\"Ollidar\">Ollidar</a> (5)<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyonce\" title=\"Lyonce\">Lyonce</a> (5-12)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gawen\" title=\"Gawen\">Gawen</a> (12-42)<sup>3</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Myros\" title=\"Myros\">Myros</a> (42)<sup>2,</sup><sup>3</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Desmond_(Grand_Maester)\" title=\"Desmond (Grand Maester)\">Desmond</a> (42-44)<sup>3</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Benifer\" title=\"Benifer\">Benifer</a> (44-59)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elysar\" title=\"Elysar\">Elysar</a> (60-97)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Allar\" title=\"Allar\">Allar</a> (97-101)</li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Runciter</a> (101-112)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mellos\" title=\"Mellos\">Mellos</a> (112-127)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Orwyle\" title=\"Orwyle\">Orwyle</a> (127-131)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Munkun\" title=\"Munkun\">Munkun</a> (131-?)<sup>4,</sup><sup>5</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alford\" title=\"Alford\">Alford</a><sup>6</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester_(Aerys_I)\" title=\"Grand Maester (Aerys I)\">Aerys I's</a> (~210-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a> (257-258)<sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellendor\" title=\"Ellendor\">Ellendor</a> (258-259)<sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Merion\" title=\"Merion\">Merion</a> (259)<sup>7</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a> (259-300)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr styl